data.description: Welcome to this stunning home in the desired SE location! With an open floor plan, this home offers a spacious and inviting atmosphere perfect for entertaining and daily living. The main level boasts three bedrooms, Including a primary bedroom and private bathroom, providing ample space for your family or guests. Cozy up by the fireplace on chilly evenings which creates a warm and inviting ambiance. The lower level features a convenient wet bar, ideal for hosting gatherings for your favorite sporting events. The two car garage offers ample amount of storage for all your outdoor toys.  Take a step outside to the back patio which offers additional space for all your entertaining needs.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful home yours!
